Hamiltonian term in matrix form:
⎡x₀₀   0    0 ⎤
⎢             ⎥
⎢ 0   x₀₀   0 ⎥
⎢             ⎥
⎣ 0    0   x₂₂⎦

   2           2           2    
M₂ₓ ⋅x₀₀ + M_2y ⋅x₀₀ + M_2z ⋅x₂₂

Hamiltonian terms for all equivalent combinations of sites:
(2, 2):
   2           2           2    
M₂ₓ ⋅x₀₀ + M_2y ⋅x₀₀ + M_2z ⋅x₂₂

(4, 4):
   2           2           2    
M₄ₓ ⋅x₀₀ + M_4y ⋅x₂₂ + M_4z ⋅x₀₀

(3, 3):
   2           2           2    
M₃ₓ ⋅x₂₂ + M_3y ⋅x₀₀ + M_3z ⋅x₀₀

